          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="616e-c7be-abff-a2bf">Use when another Friendly Biological Unit (including a Structure) suffers Damage Within 4&quot;. Reduce the Total Damage before allocation by 2.</characteristic>
